metadata.name: Waiting For Them To Respond - Collectors Edition
metadata.description:
Sunset, warm sky  
And cars flying around  
Trying to send a message  
Waiting for someone to respond

Frozen in time  
Seeing the change all around  
Reaching out to someone out there  
Waiting for them to respond

Golden hour  
Sun is floating down  
Wish they can see it  
Waiting for someone to respond

Getting dark  
I might have to step down  
Will come back tomorrow  
Will be waiting for them to respond
